My LinkedIn


Pursuing an Accounting Major at BYU-Idaho


Drake Tax software, Structured Query Language, customer service, Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, PowerPoint), and Google Workspace (Docs, Sheets, Slides)




September 2022 - now Brigham Young University - Idaho



September 2022 - Current Full Tuition Academic Grant, BYU-Idaho


January 2025 - April 2025 Tax Intern at Thrive CPA - Tax return computation, completed tax returns for individual clients and businesses - Information organization, organized and clarified data in easy-to-understand files - Bookkeeping, completed monthly recording and organizing of the financial transactions of a business

June 2022 - September 2022 Barista at Starbucks - Customer service representative - Cashier and unique drink preparation - Certified in food safety and food sanitation techniques
